code: public void testNullPrefix() {     Exception e = expectThrows(IllegalArgumentException.class, () -> new PrefixLogger(logger, null)).     assertThat(e.getMessage(), containsString("use a regular logger")). }

public void testEmptyPrefix() {     Exception e = expectThrows(IllegalArgumentException.class, () -> new PrefixLogger(logger, "")).     assertThat(e.getMessage(), containsString("use a regular logger")). }
